<p>Exodus was <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/matthew-mcconaughey-to-make-his-video-game-debut-in-sci-fi-rpg-exodus">first announced at The Game Awards at the end of last year</a>, revealing McConaughey would be making his video game debut. We don't have a release date yet. </p>
<p>As for the developer, Archetype Entertainment, you may recall, is a <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/ex-bioware-vets-working-on-story-driven-sci-fi-game-at-new-wizards-of-the-coast-studio">video game studio from Wizards of the Coast</a>. It is headed up by two ex-BioWare veterans.</p></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
